strings: <voice_0x01000DF4><se_def>re: I was amazed to find myself at home.
<voice_0x01000DF5><se_def>re: I will never forget the day you asked me to meet your dear Sasha... Thank you very much.
<voice_0x01000DF6><se_def>re: And why have you come to my kingdom on a sunny day?
<voice_0x01000DF8><se_def>re: Over the centuries it has been one of our greatest treasures.
<voice_0x01000DF9><se_def>re: But I couldn't refuse my friends' wishes. I'm really happy.
<voice_0x01000DFA><se_def>re: It was sealed in a box. I'll take you there
<voice_0x01000DFB><se_def>re: These disciples continued from generation to generation through members of the royal family.
<voice_0x01000DFE><se_def>re: ...... I do not believe it! cautious......! that's it
<voice_0x01000DFF><se_def>re: This is definitely a thief's work! don't forgive
<voice_0x01000E00><se_def>re: ... It seems a miracle happened. Ugin was stolen
<voice_0x01000E01><se_def>re: The bad guys are probably still in the tunnel.
<voice_0x01000E02><se_def>re: It is very dangerous to hunt them. You will not enter
<voice_0x01000E03><se_def>re: My name is the palace guard. They want Vinina back! Listen well!
